---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
	title="Moveroo | Terms of Use"
	description="Review the terms and conditions governing your use of the Moveroo website and our moving services across Australia."
	canonical="https://moveroo.com.au/terms-of-use/"
>
	<section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-white via-slate-50 to-slate-100 py-24">
		<div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-6">
			<p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.35em] text-emerald-600">Terms of Use</p>
			<h1 class="mt-6 text-4xl font-semibold text-slate-900">Using the Moveroo website</h1>
			<p class="mt-6 text-base text-slate-600">
				These Terms govern your access to moveroo.com.au and outline the rights, responsibilities and limitations that apply when you use our services. By continuing to browse or interact with the site, you agree to abide by these conditions.
			</p>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="bg-white py-20">
		<div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl space-y-12 px-6 text-slate-600">
			<section class="space-y-4">
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-900">Our services</h2>
				<p>
					We work to ensure the website runs smoothly; however, temporary interruptions or changes to features may occur without notice. At times we may modify or discontinue portions of the site. We are not liable for any downtime or delays outside our control.
				</p>
			</section>

			<section class="space-y-4">
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-900">Prohibited conduct</h2>
				<p>Avoid activities that:</p>
				<ul class="ml-6 list-disc space-y-2">
					<li>Break laws or infringe on third-party rights.</li>
					<li>Harass, defame or interfere with other users.</li>
					<li>Send unsolicited communications or attempt to disrupt the site.</li>
					<li>Introduce viruses, malicious code or assist others in doing so.</li>
				</ul>
			</section>

			<section class="space-y-4">
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-900">Intellectual property</h2>
				<p>
					All site content—including design, text, images and logos—is owned or licensed by Moveroo. You may view or temporarily print content for personal reference only. Reproducing, modifying, framing or redistributing materials for commercial purposes is not permitted without written approval.
				</p>
			</section>

			<section class="space-y-4">
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-900">Third-party websites</h2>
				<p>
					We occasionally link to external websites for convenience. Moveroo does not control these third-party sites and is not responsible for their content, policies or availability. You interact with linked sites at your own risk.
				</p>
			</section>

			<section class="space-y-4">
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-900">Indemnity</h2>
				<p>
					You agree to indemnify and hold Moveroo harmless from any claims, costs or liabilities resulting from your misuse of the site or breach of these Terms.
				</p>
			</section>

			<section class="space-y-4">
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-900">Disclaimer & limitation of liability</h2>
				<p>
					We provide the site “as is” and do not warrant uninterrupted access or absence of errors. To the maximum extent allowed by law, Moveroo disclaims responsibility for any loss arising from site usage. Where guarantees cannot be excluded, our liability is limited to resupply of services or reimbursement of their cost.
				</p>
			</section>

			<section class="space-y-4">
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-900">Privacy</h2>
				<p>
					Your use of the site is also governed by the <a class="text-emerald-600 hover:text-emerald-700" href="/privacy-policy/">Privacy Policy</a>, which explains how we collect and manage personal information.
				</p>
			</section>

			<section class="space-y-4">
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-900">Termination</h2>
				<p>
					Moveroo may suspend or terminate access to the site at any time. Even after termination, provisions relating to intellectual property, liability and indemnity remain in effect.
				</p>
			</section>

			<section class="space-y-4">
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-900">Miscellaneous</h2>
				<p>
					If any clause of these Terms is deemed unenforceable, the remaining clauses stay in effect. Our decision not to act on a breach does not waive our right to enforce these Terms in the future.
				</p>
				<p>
					These Terms are governed by the laws of Queensland, Australia, and disputes are subject to the non-exclusive jurisdiction of Queensland courts.
				</p>
			</section>

			<section class="space-y-4">
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-900">Contact</h2>
				<p>
					Questions can be directed to <a class="text-emerald-600 hover:text-emerald-700" href="mailto:removals@moveroo.com.au">removals@moveroo.com.au</a>.
				</p>
			</section>
		</div>
	</section>
</Layout>
